flowchart TD
    A[User opens login page] --> B[Submit email and password]
    B --> C{Credentials valid?}
    C -->|No| D[Show login error]
    C -->|Yes| E{Role}
    E -->|Admin| F[Redirect to Admin Dashboard]
    E -->|Student| G{Profile complete?}
    G -->|No| H[Redirect to Profile Edit]
    G -->|Yes| I[Redirect to Student Dashboard]

    A --> J[Forgot Password]
    J --> K[Submit email]
    K --> L[Send reset link]
    L --> M[Open reset password page]
    M --> N[Submit new password]
    N --> O[Password updated]

    P[Public signup route is not active right now] --> A
